page.title: 06A day in my life
page.content: 7.30am-I wake up,get changed,have a wash and have breakfast 8.15am-I catch the bus and get to school in 30 minutes 9.00am-We go in for registration 9.20am-French with Mrs Hall 10.35am-Break for 15 minutes 10.50am-English with Mrs Goldie 12.05pm- Dinner time 1.20pm-Whistle goes,registration 1.30pm-Library and communication studies 2.35pm-Break for 15 minutes 2.50pm-Integrated studies 4.00pm-Home time.Do jobs.Go to park for two and a half hours 7.30pm-Come in,watch TV,read.Sometimes I stay up until the pub shuts,then I talk to the staff.My mum and dad sometimes have a drink 11.00pm-Go to bed
